               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Incipits and headings of the texts; chapter titles written in the margins; numbers of the “tituli”; parts of the Canon tables; names of the donors; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
On the incipit page of each Gospel and of Text I, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
