                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1r">Fol. 1r</locus>: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1r: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘታቦተ፡ ማርያም፡ ገናህት፡ ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳሎስ[sic]</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1r: This book is of the tabot of Maryam Gänaht. He who steals it or erases (its text) shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.</q>
                           Recent, in pencil.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#32rb">Fol. 32rb</locus>: Record concerning a commercial transaction.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
